{"tid":296641,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[尋犬]隻狗唔見左[元朗唐狗]","createTime":"2017-06-24T17:46:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T11:49:28.000Z","uid":77724,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"06854a711a6b5dca5158711b5fa89f202f391b11","tid":296641,"uid":77724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T17:46:21.000Z","msg":"幫朋友問:<br />\n<br />\n隻狗係村屋地方唔見左，佢識路返屋企但又冇返到，又驚被漁農處捉左，聽日公眾假期應該冇人聽電話，<br />\n如果真係要等到星期一先打去問，隻狗會唔會有事？<br />\n應該點做？<br />\n<br />\n晶片方面，佢話上個月帶左另一隻狗去睇醫生，<br />\n醫生check 完唔見有晶片(但之前有整過晶片)，<br />\n所以佢擔心呢隻唔知有冇。<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知星期日有冇得直接去狗場睇？<br />\n補返狗狗張相，如有元朗住村屋巴打麻煩留意下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/25/013437_8886756c27ae9a99b6898a0e2d7d2bb9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F25%2F013437_8886756c27ae9a99b6898a0e2d7d2bb9.jpg&h=b468c0f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e5059c387a8160be81c43552f997f826ec348e8e","tid":296641,"uid":77724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T19:46:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a9f88ea97dde14451ea23c84fa45f821fc147b","tid":296641,"uid":54036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T19:54:47.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5563d77ed845dcd53196568574613634fa7b98b4","tid":296641,"uid":88666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T19:57:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ad39c21c32b672525773a4cf9d980197c12d39","tid":296641,"uid":100057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T19:58:07.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc9b84030523a02538d8a5c7b708e87ee2e4bff2","tid":296641,"uid":15877,"like":0,"